b'Utsurun Desu.': b'An anime adaptation of Sensha Yoshida\'s Utsurun Desu. four-panel "nonsensical" gag comedy manga. The manga used a stable of off-the-wall characters to tell jokes that defied logic or reasoning. The original manga ran in Shogakukan\'s Big Comic Spirits magazine from 1989 to 1994. \n\n(Source: ANN)'
